snippet.title: The Jak and Daxter Collection | Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description: Set on an unnamed planet, these games follow the two protagonists, Jak and Daxter, as they try to unlock the secrets of their world and discover mysteries left behind by the Precursors. Experience all four classics on PS4 with 1080 up-rendering, Trophies, and more. Purchase and download these games from PlayStation Store.
